OL,3,CWhat to see this August: From
OL,4,Csandpipers to the Perseids meteor
OL,5,Cshower
OL,7,FThis year, our sea temperature has
OL,8,Fbeen about a degree above the long-
OL,9,Fterm average and is now hovering at
OL,10,Faround 19C.
OL,12,FAlthough dry weather tends to
OL,13,Fdominate, August can bring wetter
OL,14,Fconditions than late spring and early
OL,15,Fsummer, with an increased likelihood
OL,16,Fof thunderstorms and periods of rain
OL,17,For showers.
