OL,3,CWhat to see this August: From
OL,4,Csandpipers to the Perseids meteor
OL,5,Cshower
OL,7,FThis can happen when low-pressure
OL,8,Fsystems travel across from the west,
OL,9,Fwith warmer air temperatures allowing
OL,10,Fthe atmosphere to hold moisture.
OL,12,FOutside of these systems, August tends
OL,13,Fto be a quieter month wind-wise, with
OL,14,Fa light to moderate breeze common.
OL,16,FOur length of days in August is
OL,17,Fcomparable to April and we lose almost
OL,18,Ftwo hours from the beginning to the
OL,19,Fend of the month.
