OL,5,Cshower
OL,7,FAugust can be a good time for
OL,8,Fstargazing as the sun is setting a
OL,9,Flittle earlier, the nights are still
OL,10,Fwarm and we have an exciting meteor
OL,11,Fshower taking place.
OL,13,FThe Perseids peak overnight from
OL,14,FTuesday 12 to Wednesday 13 August.
