OL,3,CWhat to see this August: From
OL,4,Csandpipers to the Perseids meteor
OL,5,Cshower
OL,7,FIn the right conditions, it can
OL,8,Fproduce up to 100 meteors per hour.
OL,9,FThis year, it is looking a little on
OL,10,Fthe cloudy side and the waning full
OL,11,Fmoon will also reduce the visibility
OL,12,Fof these showers, which will be at 84%
OL,13,Fbrightness.
OL,15,FThis may wash out some of the meteors,
OL,16,Fbut it is still worth keeping an eye
OL,17,Fout for them during a clear spell.
OL,19,FAugust's full moon, which occurred on
OL,20,FSaturday 9 August, is known as a
OL,21,F'sturgeon moon'.
