OL,5,Cshower
OL,7,FThis is named after a giant fish
OL,8,Ftraditionally caught in the late
OL,9,Fsummer.
OL,11,FThe end of the month can also bring
OL,12,Fgreat stargazing conditions, as light
OL,13,Ffrom the moon diminishes.
OL,15,FIt will be a good time to take in the
OL,16,FMilky Way on a clear night.
