OL,3,CWhat to see this August: From
OL,4,Csandpipers to the Perseids meteor
OL,5,Cshower
OL,7,FWith hot weather to be expected in
OL,8,FAugust, it's a good idea to put out
OL,9,Fclean, fresh water for garden birds.
OL,10,FThey need to drink plenty and cool off
OL,11,Fby bathing when the temperatures climb
OL,12,Fup.
OL,14,FSmall sandpiper species - the common,
OL,15,Fgreen and wood sandpiper - can be seen
OL,16,Fpassing through the island now on
OL,17,Ftheir way south.
OL,19,FIn terms of coastal birds, puffins are
OL,20,Fstarting to depart but you may be able
OL,21,Fto spot other seabirds like gannets.
