OL,3,CWhat to see this August: From
OL,4,Csandpipers to the Perseids meteor
OL,5,Cshower
OL,7,FIt's also a good month to spot migrant
OL,8,Fgull species, like the rare Caspian
OL,9,Fgull.
OL,11,FWhen it comes to plant life, August is
OL,12,Fa vibrant month. Colourful flowers
OL,13,Flike hydrangea and sunflowers can now
OL,14,Fbe seen in bloom.
OL,16,FWatch out for weever fish, which can
OL,17,Fgive a painful sting to anyone who
OL,18,Fstands on one. The fish spend most of
OL,19,Ftheir time on the sea floor - you can
OL,20,Fsafeguard against them by wearing
OL,21,Fwaterproof shoes.
